rmance, an unnamed Raku tea bowl-each has a place here. Made whole by time and its alteration in timelessness, synchrony, coincidences, and accidents, Rain in Plural beautifully reveals an elegiac yet ever-evolving inner life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aRock musicy2011-2020. 7aPOETRY / Subjects & Themes / General.2bisacsh  aAsian poetry.  aBuddhism.  aEuropean poetry.  aGeorges Wolinski.  aautobiographical writing.  acontemporary poetics.  acontemporary poetry.  across-cultural.  aexpatriate poets.  ahistory and memory.  ahybrid writing.  aintercultural.  apoetry and spirituality.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishz978311070474708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020z9783110704532oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069008840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780691203577zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780691203577423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780691203577.jpg  a978-3-11-069008-8  PUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070474-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DKUb2020